text: Palo Alto is a town in the Mexican state of Aguascalientes. It stands at . It serves as the municipal seat for the surrounding municipalities of El Llano. As of 2010, Palo Alto had a total population of 5,399. ==References== ==External links== *http://www.aguascalientes.gob.mx/estado/m_elll.html Category:Populated places in Aguascalientes
